# Project Overview

This is a Claude Agent SDK RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation) project.

## Core Principles

- **DRY (Don't Repeat Yourself)**: Extract repeated code into reusable functions
- **Single Responsibility**: Each function should do one thing well
- **Explicit over Implicit**: Prefer clear, explicit code over magic
- **Type Safety**: Always use type annotations

---

## Project Structure

```
in_file_rag/
├── .cursor/rules/       # Cursor AI rules
├── .vscode/             # VS Code/Cursor configuration
├── data/knowledge_base/ # Knowledge base data
├── logs/                # Agent execution logs
├── venv/                # Python virtual environment
├── .env                 # Environment variables (API keys)
└── agent_rag.py         # Main agent script
```

---

## Environment

- Python 3.13+
- Virtual environment in `venv/`
- Dependencies managed via pip
- API keys stored in `.env` file

